room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: This was a great experience. We didn’t escape but we’re sooooo close. Definitely worth every penny.

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: If you are looking for something different and fun, this is it! It was great!

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: I was here for a business event. The experience was far better than I expected it would be. The puzzles weren't obvious, the situation was well presented and I will definitely be coming back with more friends.

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We recently tried Mission Mars at the Mall of America and our family had a blast (pun intended)! It was very challenging, and all enjoyed the experience, even the eight-year-old. Fun for the entire family!

room_title: Escape room "Mission: Mars" by The Escape Game Minneapolis in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We went with family and friends and had such a great time in the Mission Mars room. The hour goes by so fast because the puzzles and props clearly had a lot of thought and effort put into creating them. I can't suggest it enough, it was easily my favorite escape room I've ever done!
